{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after  the month, when they came for me, the camps, inside the camp authority were making the decision on which brigade I go.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they found me a comparatively lighter brigade to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were on Kandalaksha on the White Sea in the polar region.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Kandalaksha was-- I transfer-- translate it into English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Kandala were monocles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was a place where they were keeping prisoners in cells, as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was on the Kola peninsula, the south of the Kola peninsula.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Kola peninsula is extremely rich in minerals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they were building there-- we were--our camp was building a power station for aluminium refinery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were close-- it was supposed to be the biggest aluminium refinery in the world.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Anyway, after months working in the forest, I got pneumonia and was taken to the camp-- Lazaret was the camp, with high temperatures.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And while I was there, after a while, I was better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I had a good pair of boots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I gave the boots to somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And for this, they let me in the hospital to work as a cleaner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So at least I was warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "From working as a cleaner, I progressed and became slowly an assistant to a doctor, and started seeing patients in my own right.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then, I became the sanitary inspector for the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I had colossal powers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I was getting special food from the kitchen because I could make anybody to be thrown to out to work, you know-- which I never did.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But I had colossal authority.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I made friends with the Russian inmates, as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
